vote_average":0},{"width":2048,"height":1151,"file_path":"/7LMrLficBAkVzPQZkmiXqndebVK.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":3276,"height":1844,"file_path":"/bAbnmpW6ZIf5AeCeaCgC3UFvdew.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":2048,"height":1153,"file_path":"/16fYvW9oQsgOX0iRjdz8SEZlqgj.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":2225,"height":1252,"file_path":"/xemE1mDwxx9YA4jGG2O6lWX6sCA.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":2048,"height":1153,"file_path":"/8oQDvh39MQ2piN1KXvrjZn1LGHn.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-21T11:26:44.686+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":92,"tagline":"이제 악마까지 때려잡는다","homepage":"","overview":"악마와 그를 쫓는 어둠의 숭배자들로 인해 혼란에 빠지게 된 도시. 공권력조차 이들 앞에서 무력해지자 특별한 능력을 가진 어둠의 해결사 거룩한 밤 팀 바우, 샤론, 김군이 직접 악의 무리를 처단하고자 한다. 그러던 중 갑자기 동생 은서가 이상증세를 보인다는 의뢰인 정원이 찾아오고 그 안에서 지금껏 본 적 없던 강력한 존재의 기운을 느끼는데… 과연 거룩한 밤 팀은 악의 무리에 맞서 세상을 구원해 낼 수 있을까?"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Holy Night: Demon Hunters","runtime":92,"tagline":"Beat up to the salvation.","homepage":"","overview":"When a devil-worshipping criminal network plunges Seoul into chaos, the police turn to Holy Night—a trio of supernatural demon hunters—to restore order and defeat the rising evil."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Святая ночь: Охотник на демонов","runtime":92,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Сеул погружается в хаос, когда город захватывает криминальная сеть, члены которой поклоняются дьяволу. Полиция в отчаянии и вынуждена призвать на помощь команду охотников на демонов «Святая ночь». Сможет ли троица, на вооружении которой интеллект, мускулы и сверхъестественные способности, свергнуть власть Тьмы и восстановить порядок в городе?"},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Holy Night: Demon Hunters","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Holy Night é uma equipe que luta contra grupos que adoram demônios. Os membros da equipe da Holy Night são Bau, Sharon e Kim Gun. A habilidade especial de Bau é sua poderosa força física. Sharon tem a habilidade de identificar demônios e realizar exorcismos. Kim Gun ajuda Bau e Sharon. Enquanto isso, a psiquiatra Jung Won visita a equipe da Noite Santa para salvar sua irmã mais nova, Eun Seo. Um demônio reside no corpo de Eun Seo."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Holy Night is een team dat vecht tegen groepen die demonen aanbidden. De leden van het Holy Night-team zijn Bau (Ma Dong-Seok), Sharon (Seohyun) en Kim-kun (David Lee). Bau's speciale vaardigheid is zijn krachtige fysieke kracht. Sharon heeft het vermogen om demonen te identificeren en exorcismen uit te voeren. Kim-kun helpt Bau en Sharon. Ondertussen bezoekt psychiater Jung-won (Kyung Soo-Jin) het team van de Heilige Nacht om haar jongere zus Eun-seo (Jung Ji-So) te redden. Er verblijft een demon in het lichaam van Eunseo."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"神圣之夜：恶魔猎人","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"影片讲述狩猎恶魔的黑暗解决师“神圣之夜”团队与崇拜邪恶的犯罪集团对抗的故事。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"鐵拳驅魔","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"《犯罪都市》系列馬東石，神臂震懾魔界！ 全國多個城市均發生怪異兇殺事件，獵魔團隊「神聖之夜」的成員：以拳頭獵殺惡魔的驅魔師巴武（馬東石 飾）、擁有識別惡魔能力的莎朗（徐玄 飾）、協助舉行驅魔儀式的金君（李大衛 飾）；嗅到不尋常的邪惡氣息，決定誓師出動，聯手阻止暗黑勢力主宰世界。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"ليلة مقدسة: صائدو الشياطين","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"تغرق سيول في الفوضى مع ظهور شبكة إجرامية عبدة للشيطان. في نداء يائس للخلاص، تضطر الشرطة إلى تجنيد \"هولي نايت\"، وهم ثلاثة من صائدي الشياطين المسلحين بقوى خارقة للطبيعة. فهل سيتمكن \"هولي نايت\" من قهر حكم الشيطان وإعادة النظام إلى المدينة؟"},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"ฅนต่อยผี","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"เรื่องราวของทีมโฮลี่ไนท์ ที่ต่อสู้กับกลุ่มคนที่บูชาปีศาจ"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"聖夜：惡魔都市","runtime":0,"tagline":"現在連惡魔都要我來收拾","homepage":"https://garageplay.tw/movie/content/4917","overview":"因為崇拜邪惡的集團，使都市陷入混亂。擁有特殊能力的惡魔獵人「聖夜」團隊成員巴宇（馬東石 飾）、莎倫（徐玄 飾）、金君（李大衛 飾），他們是否戰勝邪惡力量，恢復都市的秩序呢？​"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Holy Night: Demon Hunters","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Đêm Thánh: Đội Săn Quỷ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Đêm Thánh Đội Săn Quỷ là bộ phim Hàn mới nhất với sự góp mặt của ông chú Ma Dong Seok. Seoul chìm trong hỗn loạn khi một mạng lưới tội phạm tôn thờ ma quỷ xuất hiện. Trong sự cầu xin tuyệt vọng để được cứu rỗi, cảnh sát buộc phải nhờ đến ‘Đêm Thánh’, một bộ ba thợ săn quỷ được trang bị sức mạnh siêu nhiên. Liệu ‘Đêm Thánh’ có thể chinh phục ách thống trị của quỷ dữ và khôi phục trật tự cho thành phố?"},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Свята ніч: Мисливці на демонів","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Сеул поринає в хаос, коли несподівано з’являється злочинна мережа, яка поклоняється самому дияволу. Поліція звертається до таємної команди мисливців, озброєних надприродними здібностями. Пізніше місцевий психіатр благає героїв про допомогу, щоб врятувати свою одержиму сестру. Вся команда стикається віч-на-віч із надзвичайно могутньою жахливою силою, якої ніколи не бачила."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"לילה קדוש: ציידי שדים","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"הלילה הקדוש הוא צוות שנלחם בקבוצות שסוגדות לשדים.\r חברי צוות הלילה הקדוש הם באו (מא דונג סוק), שרון (סו היון) וקים גאן (דיוויד יי).היכולת המיוחדת של באו היא הכוח הפיזי החזק שלו.\r לשרון יש יכולת לזהות שדים ומבצעת גירוש שדים.\r קים גאן עוזר לבאו ושרון.בינתיים, הפסיכיאטרית ג'אנג און (קיונג סו ג'ין) מבקרת בצוות הלילה הקדוש כדי להציל את אחותה הצעירה, און סו (ג'נג ג'י סו), ששד שוכן בגופה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Święta Noc: Łowcy Demonów","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Kiedy grupa przestępcza oddająca cześć diabłu pogrąża Seul w chaosie, policja zwraca się do Holy Night – trójki nadprzyrodzonych łowców demonów – z prośbą o przywrócenie porządku i pokonanie rosnącego zła."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"شب مقدس: شکارچیان شیطان","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Noche de paz: Cazadores de demonios","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un equipo de varias personas lucha contra espíritus malignos."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"悪魔祓い株式会社","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"本作の舞台は、悪魔崇拝のカルト集団の台頭によって混乱に陥る韓国。その混乱に立ち向かおうとした警察や神父が、バウ、シャロン、キムからなる悪魔祓いを専門で請け負う会社に駆け込む事態となっていた。そんな中、医師のジョンウォンから愛する妹ウンソを助けてほしいという切なる依頼が舞い込んでくる。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Noche de paz: Cazadores de demonios","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Holy Night: Demon Hunters","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Şeytana tapan bir suç şebekesi Seul'ü kaosa sürüklediğinde, polis düzeni yeniden sağlamak ve yükselen kötülüğü yenmek için doğaüstü şeytan avcıları üçlüsü Holy Night'a başvurur."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Светата нощ: ловци на демони","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Сеул е потопен в хаос, когато престъпна мрежа, почитаща дявола, превзема града. Полицията е отчаяна и е принудена да извика екипа за лов на демони „Светата нощ“. С ум, мускули и свръхестествени сили, може ли триото да свали Мрака и да възстанови реда в града?"},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Holy Night: Demon Hunters","runtime":92,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dans une ville plongée dans le chaos par un groupe qui vénère le mal, les sombres médiums aux capacités spéciales, l'équipe Bau, Sharon et Kim Gun luttent contre le groupe maléfique dans ce film d'action occulte."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Holy Night: Demon Hunters","runtime":91,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Seoul versinkt im Chaos eines satanistischen Verbrechernetzwerks. Die Polizei wendet sich an „Holy Night“ – drei Dämonenjäger mit Ba Woo, Exorzistin Sharon und Assistent Kim-kun. Als Psychiaterin Jung-won um Hilfe für ihre besessene Schwester Eun-seo bittet, stoßen sie auf eine dämonische Macht, die alles Bisherige übertrifft."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"68252469bf6c2054817e88f2","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/68252469bf6c2054817e88f2","author":"Chris Sawin","content":"$11","created_at":"2025-05-14T23:16:57.936Z","updated_at":"2025-05-14T23:16:58.229Z","author_details":{"name":"Chris Sawin","rating":5,"username":"ChrisSawin","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"68943daa1d34f51f6399a7b1","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/68943daa1d34f51f6399a7b1","author":"MovieGuys","content":"in spite of a strong cast of well known Korean actors, \"Holy Night Demon Hunters\" is decidedly \"meh\". \r\n\r\nThis is a mix of any exorcism film you care to think of, mashed up with your standard, hard hitting, Korean action fare. Its lightweight, rather cheesy tones fall flat, as do rather stunted attempts at humour. \r\n\r\nIn summary, a very ordinary Korean supernatural action flick, that's wholly unoriginal and unremarkable. A mediocre watch.","created_at":"2025-08-07T05:46:18.241Z","updated_at":"2025-08-07T05:46:18.314Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":6,"username":"MovieGuys","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":1224993,"adult":false,"title":"Dark Nuns","video":false,"overview":"Desperation drives two nuns to perform an exorcism no nun should attempt. With a possessed child at the mercy of evil and the opposition of the Catholic Church, they take on the dangerous forbidden rituals themselves, putting their immortal souls in grave danger. They must confront the terrifying cost of their sacrilegious actions, but one goal remains: the boy must be saved at all costs.","genre_ids":[27,9648,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8965,"vote_count":76,"poster_path":"/2Abt2GgscAGtGAXTrhH44qPhugI.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-24","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/xIB0jjWBuURB0K2Pr91VsjUNYsY.jpg","original_title":"검은 수녀들","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1380682,"adult":false,"title":"The Last Rodeo","video":false,"overview":"A retired rodeo legend risks it all to save his grandson. Facing his own painful past and the fears of his family, he enters a high-stakes bullriding competition as the oldest contestant ever. Along the way, he reconciles old wounds with his estranged daughter and proves that true courage is found in the fight for family.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1175,"vote_count":72,"poster_path":"/62nu9AEIeyDNCQ2xJabq7gwb2zR.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-22","vote_average":7.729,"backdrop_path":"/9MuwxjnVPGweFwo4cZPbXM2iRX9.jpg","original_title":"The Last Rodeo","original_language":"en"},{"id":1258151,"adult":false,"title":"Kraken","video":false,"overview":"A Russian missile submarine disappears without trace during a secret mission in the Greenland Sea. A vessel is deployed to search for it, captained by the brother of the missing submarine’s commander. The search crew is tasked with locating the submarine and preventing a top-secret weapon from falling into enemy hands. Meanwhile, a geological research operation at the North Pole awakens the Kraken, a giant deep-water monster with an incredible ability to camouflage and an uncanny intelligence. As the search party narrows in on the missing submarine, they will encounter the legendary creature of the deep.","genre_ids":[878,12,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.0436,"vote_count":35,"poster_path":"/c97Xlokfn4M6ZOQmt7OfXfLDwd5.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-17","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/k8NQUrnUtX20bCreOKyEv9J7U3S.jpg","original_title":"Kraken","original_language":"ru"},{"id":1241624,"adult":false,"title":"Ghost Train","video":false,"overview":"Da-kyung, a horror YouTuber desperate for views, uploads a video about the eerie urban legends surrounding Gwanglim Station—the site of the highest number of missing person cases in the country. The video goes viral overnight. Despite everyone's warnings, Da-kyung's thirst for views only grows stronger. But as she digs deeper, she uncovers a shocking secret behind the station…","genre_ids":[27,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.9234,"vote_count":29,"poster_path":"/rOTXYy5ScOHdaC2YMQowVwQex5s.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-09","vote_average":6.552,"backdrop_path":"/3oHIkNt8dM6gH4IDKG5W121OT2T.jpg","original_title":"괴기열차","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1216662,"adult":false,"title":"Somebody","video":false,"overview":"Swimming instructor, Young-eun is a single mom raising her 7-year-old daughter, So-hyun. However, a series of tragic events happens as So-hyun's puppy falls from the apartment and dies, and So-hyun bullies other kids in school. Despite her mom's earnest efforts to address So-hyun's mental disorder, her peculiar behavior persists. Twenty years later, Min, who works in handling unclaimed deaths, meets a new colleague, Hae-young, and they form a close bond. However, as Hae-young warmly integrates herself into Min's life, Min begins to feel uncomfortable and suspicious about her intentions.","genre_ids":[9648,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8123,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/9pNlDKn3TX67u8hHEZH4zkXPkTL.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-12","vote_average":6.688,"backdrop_path":"/cS3XRGttTVC4YPIyOC3jByznpG0.jpg","original_title":"침범","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1128936,"adult":false,"title":"The Train of Death","video":true,"overview":"Newly cancer-free, Purnama heads to a resort getaway. But her train ride quickly turns ghastly as passengers start to vanish—one carriage at a time.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.1124,"vote_count":24,"poster_path":"/entDxWSkkzcutRm5S9pRWNmvyOJ.jpg","release_date":"2024-02-01","vote_average":4.7,"backdrop_path":"/26HKF0JVYWp6kUIW1sMnYryuYtq.jpg","original_title":"Kereta Berdarah","original_language":"id"},{"id":1355666,"adult":false,"title":"Love Untangled","video":false,"overview":"A lovestruck teen plans to win the school heartthrob by going from curly to straight hair — until a new transfer student changes everything.","genre_ids":[10749,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.3337,"vote_count":164,"poster_path":"/e7jStO2xfBUAUK37LbINHd1qtgy.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-28","vote_average":8.369,"backdrop_path":"/oBcvmHD7lbaX8RZ7NXvO05fIJef.jpg","original_title":"고백의 역사","original_language":"ko"},{"id":757725,"adult":false,"title":"Shadow Force","video":false,"overview":"Kyrah and Isaac were once the leaders of a multinational special forces group called Shadow Force. They broke the rules by falling in love, and in order to protect their son, they go underground. With a large bounty on their heads, and the vengeful Shadow Force hot on their trail, one family's fight becomes all-out war.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.7036,"vote_count":269,"poster_path":"/9LCpHFXZgkqp2AWiYq0mGbfZauk.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-01","vote_average":6.353,"backdrop_path":"/lBsbWXGn9maPKGhN3fozTU3BH0r.jpg","original_title":"Shadow Force","original_language":"en"},{"id":9294,"adult":false,"title":"Phenomenon","video":false,"overview":"An ordinary man sees a bright light descend from the sky, and discovers he now has super-intelligence and telekinesis.","genre_ids":[18,10749,878,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.003,"vote_count":1297,"poster_path":"/roUYK9EXmgyDO48Qje7rZI4Qgav.jpg","release_date":"1996-07-05","vote_average":6.467,"backdrop_path":"/15JUzyooElSbMXXYl2gnHX62A7X.jpg","original_title":"Phenomenon","original_language":"en"},{"id":1236470,"adult":false,"title":"The Lost Bus","video":false,"overview":"A determined father risks everything to rescue a dedicated teacher and her students from a raging wildfire.","genre_ids":[18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.1267,"vote_count":620,"poster_path":"/zpygCOYY1DPBkeUsrrznLRN5js5.jpg","release_date":"2025-09-19","vote_average":7.088,"backdrop_path":"/1xkyq5SIemtAtzl30BEGsAvDsMp.jpg","original_title":"The Lost Bus","original_language":"en"},{"id":993784,"adult":false,"title":"Lisa Frankenstein","video":false,"overview":"In 1989, a misunderstood teenager has a high school crush — who just happens to be a handsome corpse! After a set of playfully horrific circumstances bring him back to life, the two embark on a murderous journey to find love, happiness…and a few missing body parts along the way.","genre_ids":[27,35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1377,"vote_count":537,"poster_path":"/jAW7ZdIm4HLKB3g15uMOWYNdU8r.jpg","release_date":"2024-02-07","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/tsDoiLwZyAbYewoIUDJKk1SJzTF.jpg","original_title":"Lisa Frankenstein","original_language":"en"},{"id":1038392,"adult":false,"title":"The Conjuring: Last Rites","video":false,"overview":"Paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren take on one last terrifying case involving mysterious entities they must confront.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":19.5479,"vote_count":1644,"poster_path":"/byWgphT74ClOVa8EOGzYDkl8DVL.jpg","release_date":"2025-09-03","vote_average":6.907,"backdrop_path":"/tcBX2dtkNozZ0uDLVaxXrE6rqyN.jpg","original_title":"The Conjuring: Last Rites","original_language":"en"},{"id":1151031,"adult":false,"title":"Bring Her Back","video":false,"overview":"Following the death of their father, a brother and sister are sent to live with a foster mother, only to learn that she is hiding a terrifying secret.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.1259,"vote_count":1433,"poster_path":"/1Q3GlCXGYWELifxANYZ5OVMRVZl.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-28","vote_average":7.363,"backdrop_path":"/2IIKts2A9vnUdM9tTC76B8tDmuZ.jpg","original_title":"Bring Her Back","original_language":"en"},{"id":974573,"adult":false,"title":"Another Simple Favor","video":false,"overview":"Stephanie and Emily reunite on the beautiful island of Capri, Italy for Emily's extravagant wedding to a rich Italian businessman. Along with the glamorous guests, expect murder and betrayal to RSVP for a wedding with more twists and turns than the road from the Marina Grande to the Capri town square.","genre_ids":[35,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.2129,"vote_count":492,"poster_path":"/zboCGZ4aIqPMd7VFI4HWnmc7KYJ.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-07","vote_average":5.77,"backdrop_path":"/b6e5Nss2QNoQM4wJv2VppChswNP.jpg","original_title":"Another Simple Favor","original_language":"en"},{"id":1071585,"adult":false,"title":"M3GAN 2.0","video":false,"overview":"After the underlying tech for M3GAN is stolen and misused by a powerful defense contractor to create a military-grade weapon known as Amelia, M3GAN's creator Gemma realizes that the only option is to resurrect M3GAN and give her a few upgrades, making her faster, stronger, and more lethal.","genre_ids":[28,878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.8071,"vote_count":1152,"poster_path":"/oekamLQrwlJjRNmfaBE4llIvkir.jpg","release_date":"2025-06-25","vote_average":7.27,"backdrop_path":"/cT9ZfwoPDk8JbgkessmQgxAWiaM.jpg","original_title":"M3GAN 2.0","original_language":"en"},{"id":916224,"adult":false,"title":"Suzume","video":false,"overview":"Suzume, 17, lost her mother as a little girl. On her way to school, she meets a mysterious young man. But her curiosity unleashes a calamity that endangers the entire population of Japan, and so Suzume embarks on a journey to set things right.","genre_ids":[16,18,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.9706,"vote_count":1660,"poster_path":"/yStW1TXF5s7Tbtu9KjIZEaWl6HL.jpg","release_date":"2022-11-11","vote_average":7.891,"backdrop_path":"/4tdV5AeojEdbvn6VpeQrbuDlmzs.jpg","original_title":"すずめの戸締まり","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1087891,"adult":false,"title":"The Amateur","video":false,"overview":"After his life is turned upside down when his wife is killed in a London terrorist attack, a brilliant but introverted CIA decoder takes matters into his own hands when his supervisors refuse to take action.","genre_ids":[53,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.4782,"vote_count":1495,"poster_path":"/SNEoUInCa5fAgwuEBMIMBGvkkh.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-09","vote_average":6.959,"backdrop_path":"/aD7FXrm2GErTmzrIFBntPyhAqS9.jpg","original_title":"The Amateur","original_language":"en"},{"id":1573,"adult":false,"title":"Die Hard 2","video":false,"overview":"One year after his heroics in Los Angeles, John McClane is an off-duty cop who is the wrong guy in the wrong place at the wrong time. On a snowy Christmas Eve, as he waits for his wife's plane to land at Washington Dulles International Airport, terrorists take over the air traffic control system in a plot to free a South American army general and drug smuggler being flown into the US to face drug charges. It's now up to McClane to take on the terrorists, while coping with an inept airport police chief, an uncooperative anti-terrorist squad, and the life of his wife and everyone else trapped in planes circling overhead.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.871,"vote_count":6268,"poster_path":"/ybki0UWO3OPhaM6MSniuKC7sy1R.jpg","release_date":"1990-07-03","vote_average":6.965,"backdrop_path":"/cDtefl7KGnKrDziEUXetMnztvqr.jpg","original_title":"Die Hard 2","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":763577,"adult":false,"title":"Spiritpact","video":false,"overview":"Yang Jinghua, a young heir to a family of exorcists, is left struggling alone after his parents’ deaths. Barely surviving, he encounters the wealthy and skilled exorcist Duanmu Xi while trying to fend off a spirit. After a fatal accident, Yang awakens to find himself in a contract with Duanmu Xi, marking the start of his new life.","genre_ids":[14],"popularity":0.2472,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/gQfa44P8piUHJ8A7bP6j0PXBNEy.jpg","release_date":"2018-03-11","vote_average":2.7,"backdrop_path":"/6P5Y2u2HrnOrTVQXTNDUNsJpSiS.jpg","original_title":"灵契","original_language":"zh"},{"id":675,"adult":false,"title":"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix","video":false,"overview":"Returning for his fifth year at Hogwarts, Harry is stunned to find that his warnings about the return of Lord Voldemort have been ignored. Left with no choice, Harry takes matters into his own hands, training a small group of motivated students to defend themselves against the Dark Arts.","genre_ids":[12,14],"popularity":14.5713,"vote_coun