g couple, Rosemary and Guy, moves into an infamous New York apartment building, known by frightening legends and mysterious events, with the purpose of starting a family.","genre_ids":[18,27,53],"popularity":3.5505,"vote_count":4278,"poster_path":"/uYgvlHceRFjAFbsNeMInYcLZLUb.jpg","release_date":"1968-06-12","vote_average":7.821,"backdrop_path":"/qszuXKhzYR24oRpsmh7eZaPbvL8.jpg","original_title":"Rosemary's Baby","original_language":"en"},{"id":806,"adult":false,"title":"The Omen","video":false,"overview":"A diplomatic couple adopts the son of the devil without knowing it. A remake of the classic horror film of the same name from 1976.","genre_ids":[27,9648,53],"popularity":2.1202,"vote_count":1162,"poster_path":"/kf1Qq9b32jn4umll9qD2ue5ftnh.jpg","release_date":"2006-06-06","vote_average":5.654,"backdrop_path":"/cIdt86pqHfSZQRduKh0xFvnqtwE.jpg","original_title":"The Omen","original_language":"en"},{"id":834,"adult":false,"title":"Underworld: Evolution","video":false,"overview":"As the war between the vampires and the Lycans rages on, Selene, a former member of the Death Dealers (an elite vampire special forces unit that hunts werewolves), and Michael, the werewolf hybrid, work together in an effort to unlock the secrets of their respective bloodlines.","genre_ids":[14,28,53],"popularity":3.8309,"vote_count":4290,"poster_path":"/oJaQG353uOzOqffQ5K2hg03k4Vp.jpg","release_date":"2006-01-12","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/lao4tAa7y5QX5benDMyIeeRiTCb.jpg","original_title":"Underworld: Evolution","original_language":"en"},{"id":849,"adult":false,"title":"Krull","video":false,"overview":"A prince and a fellowship of companions set out to rescue his bride from a fortress of alien invaders who have arrived on their home planet.","genre_ids":[28,12,14,878],"popularity":5.7362,"vote_count":599,"poster_path":"/izDbySIrTmID0Nh6UqcWrUvOMjU.jpg","release_date":"1983-07-29","vote_average":6.048,"backdrop_path":"/qj39KZLknYXsN3TqEyq6t4TJgy0.jpg","original_title":"Krull","original_language":"en"},{"id":490,"adult":false,"title":"The Seventh Seal","video":false,"overview":"When disillusioned Swedish knight Antonius Block returns home from the Crusades to find his country in the grips of the Black Death, he challenges Death to a chess match for his life. Tormented by the belief that God does not exist, Block sets off on a journey, meeting up with traveling players Jof and his wife, Mia, and becoming determined to evade Death long enough to commit one redemptive act while he still lives.","genre_ids":[14,18],"popularity":4.3174,"vote_count":3275,"poster_path":"/wcZ21zrOsy0b52AfAF50XpTiv75.jpg","release_date":"1957-02-16","vote_average":8.165,"backdrop_path":"/6s2BqtDvp1BMiP70zCDU5OW6hMy.jpg","original_title":"Det sjunde inseglet","original_language":"sv"},{"id":277,"adult":false,"title":"Underworld","video":false,"overview":"Vampires and werewolves have waged a nocturnal war against each other for centuries. But all bets are off when a female vampire warrior named Selene, who's famous for her strength and werewolf-hunting prowess, becomes smitten with a peace-loving male werewolf, Michael, who wants to end the war.","genre_ids":[14,28,53],"popularity":6.2678,"vote_count":6489,"poster_path":"/zsnQ41UZ3jo1wEeemF0eA9cAIU0.jpg","release_date":"2003-09-19","vote_average":6.846,"backdrop_path":"/zsgdVbuEwqZbnUN9qLGEMBYf2Zo.jpg","original_title":"Underworld","original_language":"en"},{"id":420245,"adult":false,"title":"Don't Knock Twice","video":false,"overview":"A mother desperate to reconnect with her troubled daughter becomes embroiled in the urban legend of a demonic witch.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":1.5634,"vote_count":778,"poster_path":"/rxiz9zHLrqC5JfKVPbkKBboiSzI.jpg","release_date":"2017-01-12","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/pid6eklnLNn5vy9TGdaqOVm3J6V.jpg","original_title":"Don't Knock Twice","original_language":"en"},{"id":16226,"adult":false,"title":"Lady Death","video":false,"overview":"When accused by the townspeople of being in league with the Devil, Hope finds herself in a satanic deal for her life. After refusing the terms of the deal, she transforms into the powerful Lady Death and vows to wrest control of hell from her father.","genre_ids":[14,16,27,28,878],"popularity":1.5143,"vote_count":90,"poster_path":"/xVK9NOhb2jhkVqzTOjjnrQ3BUxk.jpg","release_date":"2004-07-24","vote_average":7.089,"backdrop_path":"/pP2FrpQdeUYHo7oYT59IEzkuozT.jpg","original_title":"Lady Death","original_language":"en"},{"id":16235,"adult":false,"title":"Amityville II: The Possession","video":false,"overview":"Anthony and Dolores Montelli, along with their four children, move into their dream house in Amityville and are immediately plagued by a string of paranormal experiences. When the abusive Anthony wrongly places the blame on their children, Dolores recruits a local Catholic priest to exorcise the house.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":1.7405,"vote_count":394,"poster_path":"/xx9K2m2Arr5EZUQtmggKtEK1f2a.jpg","release_date":"1982-09-24","vote_average":5.761,"backdrop_path":"/vsZUdpngUDvPfFjixjdSJR2OI0H.jpg","original_title":"Amityville II: The Possession","original_language":"en"},{"id":16373,"adult":false,"title":"The Uninvited","video":false,"overview":"A pair of siblings from London [Ray Milland and Ruth Hussey] purchase a surprisingly affordable, lonely cliff-top house in Cornwall, England. Only to discover that it actually carries a ghostly price, and soon they’re caught up in a bizarre romantic triangle from beyond the grave. Rich in atmosphere, The Uninvited, directed by Lewis Allen, was groundbreaking for the seriousness with which it treated the supernatural, haunted house genre, and it remains an elegant and eerie experience, featuring a classic score by Victor Young. A tragic family past, a mysteriously locked room, cold chills, bumps in the night - this gothic Hollywood classic has it all.","genre_ids":[9648,27,14,10749],"popularity":0.844,"vote_count":227,"poster_path":"/uwp5ahLmWliRyX3mPoLHU7